data.description: This home built in 1961 is a spacious, ranch style home with an all brick exterior. The attached 2-car garage and fenced yard compliment the exterior as well as the large concrete driveway and patio in the back yard.  Features a formal front room, large family/dining room combo with additional living space in the lower level.  Current owner uses it as an office, however, is multi-functional.  Don't miss this great home to make your very own.  Seller is offering a $500 flooring allowance for the entry/hallway and a home warranty by HomeGard.
